This document was created to analyze NCRMP BMU data

1 Data exploration

1.1 BAR data

1.1.1 Summary

There are a total of 161 bars included in this study. Sites are divided at three levels across 2 basins. The highest level (loc1) includes 2 large regions including:
caribbean, samoa

Within these larger regions are 6 sublevels (loc2) that are generally inclusive of an island including:
saintJohn, puertoRico, saintThomas, ofu, tau, tutuila

Most islands or loc2 level includes multiple sites (loc3) within it, totaling 21 loc3 levels across both basins

Deployment dates ranged from 2017-08-14 to 2022-05-20 and recovery dates ranged from 2023-05-18 to 2023-08-01. The deployment duration ranged from 365 to 2168 days and was on 801.9937888 days.
